{"tid":548942,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[歪理] 點樣可以計算一個人值幾多錢？","createTime":"2018-02-03T06:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T07:45:49.000Z","uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9eeeb14464c2a83eb68e089e94e8ebd4ed9de48","tid":548942,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:36:19.000Z","msg":"公司都有得計估值啦，點解人命冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人命估值模型：<br />\n1. 種族人口密度，愈高愈唔值錢 (eg. 北歐人 &gt; 美國人 &gt; 日本人 &gt; 中國人 = 非洲人 &gt; 印度人)<br />\n2. 個人生產力 / 全球人均 GDP<br />\n3. 個人資產淨值 / 全球人均資產淨值<br />\n4. 個人負債率 / 全球人均負債率<br />\n5. 個人現金流 / 全球人均現金流<br />\n6. 個人在居住地嘅地位 (eg. 香港地產家族 &gt; 一般市民)<br />\n7. 特權指標 (eg. 香港地產家族 &gt; 特首 &gt; 有外地居留權人士 &gt; 得張香港身份證嘅人)"},{"pid":"636cc358f9cd0cb109d318dd99d996dd3723c10d","tid":548942,"uid":166857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"IT狗最值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844250c0af069075e76129c3c8534a8f040cdd2b","tid":548942,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"636cc358f9cd0cb109d318dd99d996dd3723c10d","tid":548942,"uid":166857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"IT狗最值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"喺香港，IT 狗多啲定醫生多啲？"},{"pid":"326c6557a6ebcbf9f475acef909878c24de317bb","tid":548942,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T07:38:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffaf440389b22fb49ed9c61a145748e3ae220b28","tid":548942,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://crashstats.nhtsa.dot.gov/Api/Public/ViewPublication/812206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcrashstats.nhtsa.dot.gov%2FApi%2FPublic%2FViewPublication%2F812206&d=uX%2BhsQGbvnpEibZKVEW